# Reference Material Rules

If any `reference-material/` or internal staging folder exists in this repository:

- **Read-Only**: Never modify, overwrite, or delete files in it.
- **Internal only**: Do not mention or reference it in public-facing documentation.
- **No copy-paste**: Always synthesize content from reference material into original notes in the topic folders.

## Zero-Copy Policy

### Good Synthesis (Accepted)

- Demonstrates understanding in your own words
- Uses different vocabulary
- Shows original thinking and interpretation

### Bad Synthesis (Rejected)

- Word-for-word copying
- Minor rephrasing without understanding
- Close paraphrasing of source text

**Reference**: See `01_educational-content-rules.mdc` for the full zero-copy policy.
